        "best": "Lead with operations, not income. 'Here's exactly what happens when something goes wrong: [specific process]. You'll have a Slack channel with named contacts. Monthly statements arrive on the 1st-5th. Quarterly calls. You'll never be chasing us for an update.' Show the communication model before the income model.",
